LuaScript:
function onload()
    scoreBoard = nil
    playerBoards = {}
    playerMarkers = {}
    buttonDeal = nil
    allObjects = getAllObjects()
    markerBagRed = nil
    markerBagBlue = nil
    markerBagPurple = nil
    markerBagYellow = nil
    markerBagBlack = nil
    markerRed = nil
    markerBlue = nil
    markerPurple = nil
    markerYellow = nil
    markerBlack = nil
    for o, object in ipairs(allObjects) do
        if object.hasTag("pb_red") then table.insert(playerBoards, object) end
        if object.hasTag("pb_blue") then table.insert(playerBoards, object) end
        if object.hasTag("pb_purple") then table.insert(playerBoards, object) end
        if object.hasTag("pb_yellow") then table.insert(playerBoards, object) end
        if object.hasTag("scoreboard") then scoreBoard = object end
        if object.hasTag("m_red") then table.insert(playerMarkers, object) end
        if object.hasTag("m_blue") then table.insert(playerMarkers, object) end
        if object.hasTag("m_purple") then table.insert(playerMarkers, object) end
        if object.hasTag("m_yellow") then table.insert(playerMarkers, object) end
        if object.hasTag("b_deal") then buttonDeal = object end
        if object.hasTag("Disable") then object.interactable = false end
        if object.hasTag("smb_red") then markerBagRed = object end
        if object.hasTag("smb_blue") then markerBagBlue = object end
        if object.hasTag("smb_purple") then markerBagPurple = object end
        if object.hasTag("smb_yellow") then markerBagYellow = object end
        if object.hasTag("smb_black") then markerBagBlack = object end
        if object.hasTag("sm_red") then markerRed = object end
        if object.hasTag("sm_blue") then markerBlue = object end
        if object.hasTag("sm_purple") then markerPurple = object end
        if object.hasTag("sm_yellow") then markerYellow = object end
        if object.hasTag("sm_black") then markerBlack = object end
    end
    local boardColors = {
        {58,29,29,255},
        {30,36,59,255},
        {57,49,28,255},
        {47,30,59,255},
    }
    local boardPosition = Vector(30,0.06,37.5)
    for b, board in ipairs(playerBoards) do
        board.setScale({60,0.1,45})
        board.setColorTint({boardColors[b][1]/255,boardColors[b][2]/255,boardColors[b][3]/255,boardColors[b][4]/255})
        if b == 1 then board.setPosition(Vector(-boardPosition.x,boardPosition.y,-boardPosition.z)) end
        if b == 2 then board.setPosition(Vector(boardPosition.x,boardPosition.y,-boardPosition.z)) end
        if b == 3 then board.setPosition(Vector(-boardPosition.x,boardPosition.y,boardPosition.z)) end
        if b == 4 then board.setPosition(Vector(boardPosition.x,boardPosition.y,boardPosition.z)) end
    end
    --scoreBoard.addContextMenuItem("createsnaps", createSnaps)
    --scoreBoard.addContextMenuItem("deletesnaps", deleteSnaps)
    playerVariables = {
        {board = playerBoards[1], marker = playerMarkers[1], score = 0},
        {board = playerBoards[2], marker = playerMarkers[2], score = 0},
        {board = playerBoards[3], marker = playerMarkers[3], score = 0},
        {board = playerBoards[4], marker = playerMarkers[4], score = 0}
    }
    createSnaps()
    createLabels()
    scoreLoop()
    local dealButtonParameters = {
        click_function = "dealCardsLoop",
        function_owner = Global,
        label          = "DEAL 5\nCARDS",
        position       = {0, 0.55, 0},
        rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
        width          = 600,
        height         = 600,
        font_size      = 150,
        color          = {1,1,1},
        font_color     = {0,0,0},
    }
    buttonDeal.createButton(dealButtonParameters)
    dealIndex = 1
    dealPositions = {
        Vector(-6.00, 0.12, -10.00),
        Vector(-1.99, 0.12, -10.00),
        Vector(2.03, 0.12, -10.00),
        Vector(6.01, 0.12, -10.00),
        Vector(10.00, 0.12, -10.00)
    }
    registeredDeck = nil
    local findDeck = findCast(Vector(-10,5,-10),Vector(1,1,1),1)
    for f, found in ipairs(findDeck) do
        if found.hit_object.tag == "Deck" then
            registeredDeck = found
            found.hit_object.randomize()
        end
    end
    printToAll("[83706c][SAGANI[-]]: Lock placed cards. Use the right-click [b]Score Card[/b] function to score cards and return your tokens. Cacophony tokens automatically subtract 2 points - Do not put them in your bag.")
    Wait.frames(function() refillDiscs() end, 20)
    Wait.frames(function() dealCardsLoop() end, 40)

end

function refillDiscs()
    local targetDisc = nil
    local targetBag = nil
    local heightOffset = 0.2
    for i=1, 5, 1 do
        if i == 1 then targetDisc = markerRed targetBag = markerBagRed end
        if i == 2 then targetDisc = markerBlue targetBag = markerBagBlue end
        if i == 3 then targetDisc = markerPurple targetBag = markerBagPurple end
        if i == 4 then targetDisc = markerYellow targetBag = markerBagYellow end
        if i == 5 then targetDisc = markerBlack targetBag = markerBagBlack end
        for v=1, 24, 1 do
            local bagPosition = Vector(targetBag.getPosition()):add(Vector(0,0.5 + (heightOffset * v),0))
            local clonedDisc = targetDisc.clone()
            clonedDisc.setPositionSmooth(bagPosition)
        end
        targetDisc.destruct()
    end
end

function onObjectLeaveContainer(container, object)
    if object.hasTag("sm") then
        Wait.frames(function() object.use_snap_points = true end, 50)
    end
    if container.tag == "Deck" then
        local snaps = {}
        local ovx = 0.65
        local ovz = 1
        local snapOffsets = {
            {-ovx, 0, -ovz},
            {-ovx, 0,   0},
            {-ovx, 0,  ovz},
            {0,   0, -ovz},
            {0,   0,   0},
            {0,   0,  ovz},
            {ovx, 0, -ovz},
            {ovx, 0,   0},
            {ovx, 0,  ovz},
        }
        for o, offset in ipairs(snapOffsets) do
            local newSnap = {position=Vector(offset), rotation={0,0,0}, rotation_snap=false}
            table.insert(snaps, newSnap)
        end
        object.setSnapPoints(snaps)
        object.addContextMenuItem("Score Card", scoreCard)
    end
end

function scoreCard(player_color, position, object)
    local playerCacophonyPositions = {
        red =    Vector(-4.65, 0.5, -17.05),
        blue =   Vector(4.65,  0.5, -17.05),
        purple = Vector(4.65,  0.5,  17.05),
        yellow = Vector(-4.65, 0.5,  17.05)
    }
    local foundObjects = findCast(object.getPosition(),Vector(3,3,3),3)
    local heightOffset = 0
    local targetBag = nil
    for o, object in ipairs(foundObjects) do
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sm_red") then targetBag = markerBagRed end
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sm_blue") then targetBag = markerBagBlue end
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sm_purple") then targetBag = markerBagPurple end
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sm_yellow") then targetBag = markerBagYellow end
        if object.hit_object.hasTag("sm") then
            if object.hit_object.hasTag("sm_black") then
                local cacophonyPosition = Vector(0,0,0)
                if player_color == "Red" then cacophonyPosition = playerCacophonyPositions.red end
                if player_color == "Blue" then cacophonyPosition = playerCacophonyPositions.blue end
                if player_color == "Purple" then cacophonyPosition = playerCacophonyPositions.purple end
                if player_color == "Yellow" then cacophonyPosition = playerCacophonyPositions.yellow end
                local cacophonyTokenPosition = cacophonyPosition:add(Vector(0,0.2 * heightOffset, 0))
                object.hit_object.setPositionSmooth(cacophonyTokenPosition)
                heightOffset = heightOffset + 1
            else
                local bagPosition = Vector(targetBag.getPosition()):add(Vector(0, 1 + (0.5 * heightOffset), 0))
                object.hit_object.setPositionSmooth(bagPosition)
                heightOffset = heightOffset + 1
            end
        end

    end
    if object.getLock() == true then
        object.setLock(false)
    end
    object.flip()
    Wait.time(function() object.setLock(true) end, 1, 1)
end


function dealCardsLoop()
    dealIndex = 1
    Wait.time(function() dealCards() end, 0.1, 5)
end

function dealCards()
    local findDeck = findCast(Vector(-10,5,-10),Vector(1,1,1),1)
    local deck = nil
    for f, found in ipairs(findDeck) do
        if found.hit_object.tag == "Deck" then
            deck = found.hit_object
        end
    end
    if deck ~= nil then
        local parameters = {position=dealPositions[dealIndex], flip=true}
        deck.takeObject(parameters)
        dealIndex = dealIndex + 1
    end
end

function scoreLoop()
    Wait.time(function() scoreCounter() end, 0.5, 1)
end

function scoreCounter()
    for p, player in ipairs(playerVariables) do
        cards = findCast(player.board.getPosition(),Vector(60,10,45),3)
        local localScore = 0
        for c, card in ipairs(cards) do
            if card.hit_object.hasTag("m_sub") then
                localScore = localScore - 2
            end
            if card.hit_object.is_face_down then
                if card.hit_object.getGMNotes() ~= nil or "" then
                    local value = tonumber(card.hit_object.getGMNotes())
                    if value ~= nil then
                        if type(value) == "number" then
                            localScore = localScore + value
                        end
                    end
                end
            end
        end
        if player.score ~= localScore then
            player.score = localScore
            player.marker.editButton({index=0, label=tostring(player.score)})
            local boardSnaps = scoreBoard.getSnapPoints()
            if player.score > 0 then
                local markerPosition = Vector(0,0,0)
                if player.score > 79 then
                    markerPosition = Vector(scoreBoard.positionToWorld(boardSnaps[79].position))
                else
                    markerPosition = Vector(scoreBoard.positionToWorld(boardSnaps[player.score].position))
                end
                markerPosition:add(Vector(0,2,0))
                player.marker.setPositionSmooth(markerPosition)
            else
                player.marker.setPositionSmooth(Vector(-7.00, 2, -6.90))
            end
        end
    end

    Wait.time(function() scoreLoop() end, 0.5, 1)
end

function findCast(pos,size,type)
    local hitList = Physics.cast({
        origin       = pos,
        direction    = {0,-0.01,0},
        type         = type,
        size         = size,
        max_distance = 100,
        debug        = false,
    })
    return hitList
end

function createSnaps()
    scoreBoard.setSnapPoints({})
    --local snapPosition = Vector(0.87,0,0.87)
    local snapPosition = Vector(1.015,0,1.015)
    local snapOffsets = Vector(0.145,0,0.145)
    local snapPositions = {}
    for z = 1, 11, 1 do
        local snapRow = {}
        for x = 1, 13, 1 do
            local newSnap = {position=Vector(snapPosition.x - (snapOffsets.x * x), snapPosition.y + snapOffsets.y, snapPosition.z - (snapOffsets.z * z)), rotation={0,0,0}, rotation_snap=false}
            table.insert(snapRow, newSnap)
        end
        table.insert(snapPositions, snapRow)
        snapRow = {}
    end
    local boardSnaps = {}
    local cellTable = {
        {1,3},{1,4},{1,5},{2,5},{2,6},{2,7},{1,7},{1,8},{1,9},{2,9},
        {2,10},{2,11},{1,11},{1,12},{1,13},{2,13},{3,13},{4,13},{5,13},{5,12},
        {5,11},{4,11},{4,10},{4,9},{5,9},{5,8},{5,7},{4,7},{4,6},{4,5},
        {5,5},{5,4},{5,3},{4,3},{4,2},{4,1},{5,1},{6,1},{7,1},{8,1},
        {8,2},{8,3},{7,3},{7,4},{7,5},{8,5},{8,6},{8,7},{7,7},{7,8},
        {7,9},{8,9},{8,10},{8,11},{7,11},{7,12},{7,13},{8,13},{9,13},{10,13},
        {11,13},{11,12},{11,11},{10,11},{10,10},{10,9},{11,9},{11,8},{11,7},{10,7},
        {10,6},{10,5},{11,5},{11,4},{11,3},{10,3},{10,2},{10,1},{11,1},
    }
    for c, cell in ipairs(cellTable) do
        table.insert(boardSnaps, snapPositions[cell[1]][cell[2]])
    end
    scoreBoard.setSnapPoints(boardSnaps)
end

function deleteSnaps()
    scoreBoard.setSnapPoints({})
end

function createLabels()
    for p, player in ipairs(playerVariables) do
        local scoreDisplayParameters = {
            click_function = "nothing",
            function_owner = Global,
            label          = "0",
            position       = {0, 0.55, 0},
            rotation       = {0, 180, 0},
            width          = 0,
            height         = 0,
            font_size      = 400,
            color          = {0, 0, 0},
            font_color     = {1, 1, 1},
        }
        player.marker.createButton(scoreDisplayParameters)
    end
end
